The highest-priced setting in this guide. A princess cut center in a setting designed with oval-cut accent diamonds — the oval accent shapes create a different visual vocabulary than the square princess cut center. Oval accents in platinum: oval brilliant cuts scatter warmth well; H-color oval accents are acceptable here. The setting's premium price point reflects the architectural complexity of integrating oval accent forms into the platinum structure. With G-VS1 = **$9,566 total**. With G-VS2 = **$9,242 total**.

